message.body: Having fun with the girls?
We just finished and said bye.
The food was good.
How was moving furniture?
Right on time for Cinderella's limit
Hahahah gotta follow those magical rules now.
It went well. Book shelf and dresser are relocated. I went back to take my brother grocery shopping and nite finding up laundry
Now*
I wasn't bored earlier. I was just exhausted from the cold going straight to my head. Forgot my trapper hat to keep it warm
Look at you, so domestic!
I wonder what magical rules don't apply to you =P
Where did you get dinner?
PYT
That's fun. I think you mentioned having wanted to try a few of their burgers early on
I had this tonight:
ï¿¼

I feel sick right now.
Get cozy and bundle up
Ugh you realize who you're talking to right?
That already done.
Lol yeah I forgot. I have 2 follow up questions from the conversation we had the other night.
I'm in my sweats and under my comforter.
*that's

This is sad and cute at the same time
What are the questions?
Awww she's adorable!
But that is sad.
I've never asked anyone and it may make me seem relatively self conscious but do you think I'm attractive and did I ever have a chance
Yes you are, and that's hard for me to say because I'm not in that mental state (like I discussed the other night), so I just don't reallllly think about it with anyone.
Roger that. Thanks for the thoughts :D
Anytime.
Have you had speculoos before?
I don't think I have, and I saw your Facebook post hahah!
It's some crazy stuff. It's a Belgian cookie crumble spread. It's one of those things I wish were healthy enough to consume daily
So it's not a solid cookie?
Not from what I know it as http://www.traderjoes.com/fearless-flyer/article/561 by far my favorite
That sounds intriguing.
I don't know about cookies being in a spread though. That doesn't sound very smooth.
It has a bit roughness to it but it's negligible against the pure delight of the flavor.
It isn't crunchy but it definitely isn't smooth
Hmmm, guess the Belgians are doing it right. They knows their dessert spreads hahahah.
I'll introduce it to you eventually
Mhmm
Or I could just go to Trader Joe's...
What happens if you don't enjoy it lol
Then I blame you.
I would continue to blame your fault taste buds
Why would you pick on things smaller than you? That's just mean.
Viruses are smaller than me. I'm completely fine with making fun of them
There's a word for that, and it is bullying.
Are you gonna go tell mommy on me now?
Well there's no hope for you, you're already former.
*formed
That's unfortunate. You're giving up on me already?
You've given up on yourself.
Perhaps. It happens with lack of inspiration.
Then go get that inspo man.
Sorry. Amazon has it on back order
Get on that waiting list.
Working on it. What's the first place you'd like to go on vacation after starting this job?
Why would I go on vacation after I start a job?
Not right away. I meant like. When it were appropriate to take pto
Hahah I knew what you meant.
Ummm, if I could afford it, probably Europe.
That would be fun. It's a lot of planning so far. I need to find out the next place sis and I are staying at
Did I ask you if you were interested in making a group care package for Uyen?
I think Google is becoming smarter. YouTube recommended I watch game of thrones lore lol.
No friggin' way!
That's amazing.
Just more proof that technology is taking over!
Good morning!
Sorry, I fell asleep again last night without being ready (with my makeup on nonetheless argh)! I think you me mentioned it. I'm planning to put one together too.
I'll be cleaning my place today. First I'm packing up more of my things from parent's. Didn't get everything with my bookshelf last night.
It's ok. I can only imagine how tired you were heh
Queen - Love of my life (Rock Montreal 1981) - HD 720: https://youtu.be/vNsEEvRMtGI One of my favorites from them. Hope you enjoy.
